  "whatsapp_greeting": "Hi \u2014 I\u2019m Xhibitly\u2019s exhibit design guide. I can help you plan your booth, recommend exact products from the catalog, and get your project quote-ready. To start, what booth size are you planning: 10x10, 10x20, or 20x20?",
